</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="control-prop">
<db:title>[read-only] control : ToggleButton</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-extras-togglebutton.xml">ToggleButton</db:link> that this style is attached to.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="inactiveGradient-prop">
<db:title>inactiveGradient : Gradient</db:title>
<db:para>The gradient that is displayed on the inactive state indicator. The inactive state indicator will be the checked gradient when the button is unchecked, and the unchecked gradient when the button is checked.</db:para>
